# 2026-06-03 22:54:11.901064
+
+Fix the UI in i2m-frontend/src/pages/ProductStudio.tsx:
+
+PROBLEMS TO FIX:
+1. BUTTONS TOO BIG — Change all action buttons (primary CTA buttons like 'วิเคราะห์สินค้า', 'สร้างรูป', 'สร้างวิดีโอ'):
+   - py-4 → py-2
+   - text-xl → text-xs 
+   - shadow-md → shadow-sm
+   - Use smaller text and padding. Buttons should be compact.
+
+2. PRESET STYLE ICONS TOO BIG / OLD-FASHIONED — The Image Presets section (around line 400-440):
+   - Remove the large Material Symbols icons (style={{ fontVariationSettings... }})
+   - Instead of big cards with icons, use compact pills/badges 
+   - Each preset should be a small pill button with just text name (like: [ถือสินค้า] [ใช้งาน] [ไลฟ์สไตล์] [Close-up] [รีวิว])
+   - Remove the gradient background on preset cards, use simple border/transparent instead
+   - No large shadow, just subtle border
+
+3. VIDEO BUTTON DUPLICATION — The 'สร้างวิดีโอ' button should:
+   - Only appear ONCE, after at least one image has been generated
+   - Remove the video button from the generation section if it's duplicated anywhere
+   - Place it as a single button below the generated images grid
+
+4. GENERAL UI — Make the overall interface more compact:
+   - Reduce spacing/margins where excessive
+   - Make headers smaller
+   - Use smaller font sizes for labels
+
+IMPORTANT: Keep all existing functionality (pill selectors, editable prompt, analysis, image generation, video generation) - just change the visual styling to be more compact and modern.
+

